Variant1Text: Houston calling Linda. Houston calling Linda. Where are you you spacewalker. ^^
Variant2Text:
Helloo Linda,

I saw you walking in the coffee direction. That's a good direction to go to, generally ^^', but I would appreciate an answer.

Get back to me,
Jess
